assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: Kato Sangyo Co., Ltd. engages in the general food wholesaling business in Japan and internationally. The company's products include ambient temperature processed foods, frozen/chilled foods, confectionery, alcoholic beverages, etc. It also manufactures and sells food products, including Kanpy jams, fine foods for gourmets, pasta, processed tomato products, dried foods, condiments, grocery items, etc., as well as homemade dishes. In addition, the company offers retail support and logistics solutions. Kato Sangyo Co., Ltd. was founded in 1945 and is headquartered in Nishinomiya, Japan.
